Collaboration Model
This project follows a 50/50 partnership model:

All major decisions are made jointly
Both contributors have equal rights to review and merge changes
Work is divided based on availability and expertise, not hierarchy
All commits and pull requests are reviewed by the other collaborator before merging


How We Work

Changes are developed on separate branches
A pull request is opened for every meaningful change
The other collaborator reviews and approves before merging
Releases are tagged only when both contributors agree


